issue.title: o is undefined at golang roadmap
issue.body:
### What is the URL where the issue is happening

https://roadmap.sh/golang

### What browsers are you seeing the problem on?

Firefox

### Describe the Bug

There was an error.
Try loading the page again. or submit an issue on GitHub with following:

o is undefined
$@https://roadmap.sh/_astro/index.gjAxZpWu.js:1:4564 

### Output from browser console (if any)

Cookie “__roadmapsh_jt__” has been rejected for invalid domain.

### Participation

- [ ] I am willing to submit a pull request for this issue.

comment.body: This has been fixed now, thank you for reporting!
